20. CTA interface
-----------------
The IRF loaders now check the existence of the file before loading, and now throws
appropriate error messages in case that the files do not exist (#1586).

Only manadatory columns are read by GCTAEventsList, while any other columns will only
be stored for back writing in a FITS file.


21. COMPTEL interface
---------------------
None
